# PublicAPIExportStrategy

The export strategy to use

UPLOAD_WORKFLOW:
UAI uploads exported data
via a workflow integration

DOWNLOAD_GCS:
Download exported data via
a download link


## Values

| Name              | Value             |
| ----------------- | ----------------- |
| `DOWNLOAD_GCS`    | DOWNLOAD_GCS      |
| `UPLOAD_WORKFLOW` | UPLOAD_WORKFLOW   |
